narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: How to write and present my own research.
The thought process that goes into and general time frame of writing up research and re-writing it and giving feedback to other people's work and re-writing your own again.

narratives.question_text: How well did the knowledge, skills, and insights gained in this class align with your expectations?
comments: They were exactly as i expected.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of the course and how could it be improved?
comments: The course was great. No additions necessary.
I appreciate the continuous feedback and the set schedule of submission. It helped me become more disciplined. I also appreciate the feedback on presentations.

narratives.question_text: What advice would you give to a student considering taking this class?
comments: Stay self motivated and be proactive about your research.
Take it. You'll improve your writing and presenting skills so much.
